. Dangerous for solo players.Runners, they are on fire and waving a grenade...if they reach you they hold the grenade in their mouth and strike a Cross pose and explode. If you kill them, their bodies still explode...this is very likely to kill groups in scripted wave events, as you are typically croweded trying to rez a player or two who just had a run in with a pack of skeletons...and their blast radius is big and powerful.???These are all I've encountered so far."
