,Recommended,227100,9295851,"Posted: 28 February, 2014",all,Schiz0id,"WOWWhere to begin?First of all, I've played most of the zombie games. You should know right now that I'm an oldschool doom fan, brutal doom is my favorite game. I've also loved the stalker series, and have played left 4 dead 2, killing floor, you name it. But don't let the ""sniper game with zombies"" title fool you- this game is a hardcore shooter.The undead in this game are relentless and walk like Romero zombies. They are, however, magically induced and not virus-induced, so don't be surprised to see some occult gibberish and super zombies, skelletons, etc.The sheer amount of zombies in this game is incredible. The game loads as you play, so loading screens are very seldom seen. Also, the game is quite playable on bad systems. I think the shooting is fantastic, the smg's feel great and are varied, each gun has its advantages and disadvantages. The snipers feel great, and the x-ray deathcam, while only available in singleplayer, is simply wonderful!I really think this is a good game, but if you're expecting a non-scary breezy game, then I'm sorry to tell you this; this game is actually quite scary and tense at times. The hoarde can be scaled to fit 1-4 people amounts in single player, which I think was added since some of the poor reviews were writte, so look out for that. But the zombies in this game really do get the slip on you, and since they are magical, if you fail to hit the head they will be re-ressurrected! so BE SURE TO GET HEADSHOTS!The ammo is plentiful if you take the time to search every body. The ppsh has the most ammo, and it's quite normal to find 71 rounds for the ppsh on bodies 1 out of 5 times, I'd say.I really love this game. Get the first one first, though; the second one is kind of different, with its color filters and such. it isn't as realistic in its depiction, so start with this game first and get a feel for the world.I would give this game 4.5 out of five stars. The .5 is because the game feels simple at times, but hey, I'm a freaking doom fan so that's great to me!So get the game. It's really cheap when it goes on sale!"
